text: Ogorzelec may refer to the following places in Poland: *Ogorzelec, Kamienna Góra County in Gmina Kamienna Góra, Kamienna Góra County in Lower Silesian Voivodeship (SW Poland) *Ogorzelec, Polkowice County in Gmina Grębocice, Polkowice County in Lower Silesian Voivodeship (SW Poland)
title: Ogorzelec
